questions.quote: Yeah-yeah, I told her about the time you got drunk and fell asleep with your head in the toilet.
Yeah, but, y'know, it's... it would be like starting on the fifteenth date.
I am so sorry you got caught in the middle of that. I didn't mean to be so out there. I am furious with him!
Yes! And he said really mean things that were only partly true.
Okay, fine I admit it! I feel terrible! Would you please rub this on my chest?
I am on fire! Chandler : Listen...this is really nice. Do you... Did you write a cheque to Monica for two thousand dollars? Did Monica borrow money from you?

But uh Ross, Ross is a great guy! I was roommates with him in college. Uh, funny story... You're roommate in college died didn't he?
